item.title: CVE-2022-2092|2024-08-03T00:24:44.204Z -- unknown -- woocommerce%20pdf%20invoices%20%26%20packing%20slips

item.title: CVE-2022-2537|2024-08-03T00:39:08.074Z -- unknown -- woocommerce%20pdf%20invoices%20%26%20packing%20slips
item.description: The WooCommerce PDF Invoices & Packing Slips WordPress plugin before 3.0.1 does not sanitise and escape some parameters before outputting them back in an attributes of an admin page, leading to Reflected Cross-Site Scripting.
